OpenMP parallelisation version  of the FDM code to utilise CPU cores on each node
================================================================================

Prerequisites:
1) MPI libraries with Fortran bindings

1) In the Makefile, set the following environment variables to appropriate compilers
MPIF90, MPICC , FF90 , CC

2) In the Makefile, set the following environment variable to MPI installation respectively
MPI_INSTALL_PATH

3) Running 'make' should compile the code

4) mpirun -np X ./disfd # would launch simulation with X processes and appropriate number of threads on each node

